"``setup-kolab`` bootstrap utility is run."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/deployment-guide/localhost.rst:50
msgid ""
"A single server runs all services related to Kolab, including the LDAP, "
"SMTP, IMAP, HTTP and MySQL servers."
msgstr ""

